(35179, 63498, 0, 1, '華麗', '在歷經被劈腿的傷痛,寫下了這首沈重的歌曲......', '2011-05-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, '這個城市空氣非常稀薄\r\n彷彿充滿罪惡的枷鎖\r\n這個天空灰暗得朦朧\r\n冰冷的雨像針刺進我的胸口\r\n\r\n為什麼每個人都沒有表情\r\n為什麼心裡面充滿黑色血液\r\n我要帶著滿佈血絲眼睛\r\n用把尖鑽絞爛你的心\r\n\r\n華麗的血液濺在我的外衣\r\n白裡透紅的畫面更會顯得冷靜\r\n華麗的血液濺在我的心\r\n黑與紅的交錯  慢慢在溶化中', '', 261, '', '小J', '小J', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-05-02 12:38:33', '2015-03-12 13:47:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(35180, 63498, 0, 1, 'Go For Rock N'' Roll (tribute to Guns N'' Roses)', '在漏夜排隊等待槍與玫瑰的演唱會時,看到從地平線慢慢升起的陽光,心中的所有鬱悶一掃而空,對於未來重新燃起了希望,也因為槍與玫瑰的音樂一直帶給我們力量,以及對於樂團的堅持,所以加了些他們的經典元素,寫了這首歌獻給我們的英雄-Guns N'' Roses !', '2011-05-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, '我在寧靜的大街\r\n等待著藍與黑的交界\r\n當那曙光劃成了一條線\r\n我的希望燃燒了整片天\r\n\r\n我們穿越了叢林\r\n摘下染上血色的玫瑰\r\n耳邊傳來轟然的槍聲\r\n沸騰我沈寂已久的靈魂\r\n\r\nI say hey ~ little boy\r\nTell me what''s on your mind\r\nI say hey ~ don''t be shy\r\nJust follow your dream\r\n\r\nI say go ! For Rock N'' Roll\r\n太多不真實的夢   Facing to this fucking world\r\n\r\nGo ! For Rock N'' Roll\r\n當你徬徨的時候   Knocking on the heaven''s door\r\n\r\nGo ! For Rock N'' Roll\r\n太多黑色的誘惑   Take me to this fucking world\r\n\r\nGo ! For Rock N'' Roll\r\n聽見誰在對你說   Welcome to the jungle ', '', 287, '', '小 J', 'Roxy', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-05-02 12:51:18', '2015-03-12 13:47:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(35181, 63498, 0, 1, 'Drive Me Crazy', '就是一首罵人老母的歌～', '2011-05-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'Your mama she is drive me crazy\r\nShe wants to control everything\r\nEverything just all about money\r\nWho cares about love and free\r\n\r\nMaybe I''m not the princess charming\r\nI''m not that rich but I got what you need\r\nIf you want to be my sweetie honey\r\nForget the past just following me\r\n\r\nShe drive me crazy  ( Crazy for what ? )\r\nShe drive me crazy  ( Everything )\r\nShe drive me crazy  ( Crazy for what ? )\r\nShe drive me crazy \r\nJust fuck out !', '', 199, '', '小J', 'Roxy', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-05-02 12:57:03', '2015-03-12 13:47:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(35182, 63498, 0, 1, 'Nothing At All', '這是關於一個女孩結束一段長達七年的感情,在極度傷心無助下所寫下的心情寫照', '2011-05-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'Look all around it''s so empty\r\nGive me a reason why you have to leave\r\nIt''s used to be just you and me\r\nNow I can feel the world is caveing\r\n\r\nHow many times do I have to pay\r\nHow many times do I have to wait\r\nI''m not the girl that you looking for\r\nI''m nothing at all ..... Ti''ll you walk out the door\r\n\r\nAnyone can tell me \r\nWhat a girl should be\r\nWhat kind of love can be\r\nWhat kind of love....\r\n\r\nIt''s not suppose to be\r\nYou should be here with me\r\nYou should have know\r\nI don''t want to be alone......', '', 349, '', 'Roxy', 'Roxy', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-05-02 13:06:36', '2015-03-12 13:47:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
